description:
Kahil El’Zabar’s ‘Spirit Groove’ on Spiritmuse Records is the latest musical inspiration from Kahil El’Zabar, feat. the legendary tenor sax colossus, David Murray. El’Zabar’s & Murray’s collaborative efforts span over 4 decades of exceptional explorations in the varied realms of spiritual jazz. ’Spirit Groove’ is the defining moment upon their incredible journey to meaningful, spiritual art. They’re joined by two extraordinary  talents, Emma Dayhuff on acoustic bass and Justin Dillard on synth, piano & organ. 

With ‘Sprit Groove’, Kahil El’Zabar continues on his strong success from 2019, with an outstanding performance as a leader, composer and musician, cementing his title of ‘best percussionist in the world’.  This is a phenomenal album, bringing an entirely new, elevated dimension to the spirit of groove!

Release Date: 12 JUNE 2020  - WORLDWIDE
Gatefold 2xLP  |  Gatefold CD  |  Digital 
Preorder here:
https://spiritgroove.bandcamp.com/album/kahil-elzabars-spirit-groove-ft-david-murray 

Kahil El’Zabar - multi-percussion & voice
David Murray - tenor sax
Emma Dayhuff - acoustic bass
Justin Dillard - synth, piano, organ

Art & Art Direction - Nep Sidhu

Video shooting, editing & production: Christopher Andrew, Stoptime Live, Chicago
Recorded at the Promontory, Chicago, IL
